description:
This is a 42 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation for Detachment From Over-Thinking (Anxiety / OCD / Depression)' from the channel Michael Sealey.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This meditation encourages a calm awareness of the breath, and also a gentle detachment from the habits of rumination (ie. over-thinking). This session is useful for alleviating symptoms of anxiety, OCD, and depression.
